Package gov.nih.nci.cabig.caaers.service

Interface Summary
EvaluationService This service interface is used to implement various caaers business rules.
InteroperationService This service class is used to send AE reports to the study calendar.
OrganizationService This service interface is used to build the organization domain object.
ParticipantService This service interface is used to perform various services related to the participant domain object.
ReportService This is an service class, which is used to obtain the correct address (toAddress) of a recipient.
SchedulerService This is the service interface which is used to schedule notification for report.
StudyService Interface for Services on Study related domain object
UserService This service interface is used to manage user access to the caaers UI.
